{"tid":1468104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 未 輸！] 宣佈 每個星期六為機場和理飛！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:37.000Z","uid":115194,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0eb4c8d8adb40a7170d469c97c5521bbc9386f","tid":1468104,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:21.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我正式宣佈 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每星期六為機場和理飛！！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日有太多分化黨，不過我相信大家都係有共同目標，就係想<span style=\"color: gold;\">多人到影響到機場運作之餘 又無咁多反對聲音 </span><br />\n<br />\n明白好多人罷唔到工，所以如果每個星期六集會絕對可以好似<span style=\"color: red;\">812咁塞爆機場</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信經過今日後大家可能都對強行阻遊客呢樣嘢反感，所以以人數最勝，係我地最大優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時間亦可以<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">避免旅客濟留係港連續幾日</span></span>，塞左係異地幾日真係好難怪佢地發嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上我地一早大肆宣傳，可以令佢地預早安排下，條氣都順啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每星期一塞</span></span>絕對可以做到好大效果！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">安全，有效果，仲要唔受開學返工限制</span></span>，逼到政府回應為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講句<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 我愛大家 不分化 香港人加油</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地會愈做愈好！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推我上去呀!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"06d7418f3c389930d325c03504527f29ccb05b1a","tid":1468104,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a0f4f61909f7b88b38fcdfcb27466e9fc6a2f6b6","tid":1468104,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf66555f9be8bd92c41eaaf29885ec5c7dedbc58","tid":1468104,"uid":280899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:13.000Z","msg":"係室飽機場    係包和機場   唔係佔領機場      唔係癱瘓機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466104</a>"},{"pid":"53ecc183f0de4830ab8912e21cca3e851a0c93c0","tid":1468104,"uid":115194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2e968352e596e1a2aeaba08f402699d2c04a1bdd","tid":1468104,"uid":281950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baf59e1e0ccbfe7d7d6f201e465870c4cd5bb34","tid":1468104,"uid":52354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13